notes about debian packages
==============================

search: how to build debian package

https://wiki.debian.org/HowToPackageForDebian


the fastest rebuild steps of a package is like:

 $ apt-get source foo
 $ cd foo-0.0.1
 $ sudo apt-get build-dep foo
 $ debuild -i -us -uc -b


